      "raw_text": "LOS ANGELES, Sept. 7,-Despite\nthe appeal made to the city council\nby the board of public works to\npass an ordinance cutting the\nwages of the laborers employed by\nthe city from s225 to 81 day. the\nordinance will not be passed, and\nthe laborers viii continue to draw\n$2.25 for each days work."
    }
